title: Caller to Biden: Merry Christmas, Let's Go Brandon
author: Associated Press
description:
As President Joe Biden and first lady Jill Biden were taking phone calls Christmas Eve for NORAD's Santa tracker hotline, a father ended an otherwise pleasant conversation by telling the president, "Merry Christmas and let's go Brandon." (Dec. 24)
